main = interact $ unlines . map (show' . mspf . read) . init . lines
 where show' (n,ns) = show n ++ ": " ++ unwords (map show ns)

mspf n = (n, sort (nub (msd n)))

msd n = msd' n [] msprimes
 where
  msd' n' ds pps@(p:ps)
   | p > n = ds
   | mod n' p /= 0 = msd' n' ds ps
   | otherwise = msd' (div n' p) (p:ds) pps ++ msd' n' ds ps

msprimes = 6 : 8 : union [13,20..] [15,22..]
 where
  union xxs@(x:xs) yys@(y:ys)
   | x<=y = if ismsp x then x : union xs yys else union xs yys
   | x>y = if ismsp y then y : union xxs ys else union xxs ys
  ismsp n = null [i | i <- takeWhile (\x -> x*x <= n) msprimes, mod n i == 0]

solve :: Int -> String
solve x = show x ++ ": " ++ (unwords . map show) ans
  where

    as = filter ((== 0).(mod x)) $ takeWhile ((<= x).(^2)) msnum
    bs = map (div x) as

msnum :: [Int]
msnum = 1:6:map (+7) msnum

pns :: [Int]
pns = 6 : filter isPn (drop 2 msnum)

isPn :: Int -> Bool
isPn 1 = False
isPn x = all ((/= 0) . mod x) $ takeWhile ((<= x) . (^2)) pns

def isprime(n)
  i = 6
  while i <= Math.sqrt(n)
    return false if n % i == 0
    i += 2
    return true if not (i < n)
    return false if n % i == 0
    i += 5
  end
  return true
end

def compute(target)

  i   = 6
  while i <= target
    if target % i == 0 and isprime(i)
      ans[i] = 1
    end
    i += 2
    break unless i < target
    if target % i == 0 and isprime(i)
      ans[i] = 1
    end
    i += 5
  end
  puts "#{target}: #{ans.keys.sort.join(" ")}"
end

MAX_N = 300000

### subroutines

def msnum_generator(max_n)
  yield 6
  k = 7
  loop do
    n = k + 1
    break if n > max_n
    yield n

    n = k + 6
    break if n > max_n
    yield n

    k += 7
  end
end

def gen_msprimes(max_p, msnums)
  msprimes = (max_p + 1).times.map{false}
  msnums.each{|msn| msprimes[msn] = true}

  msps = []

  for p in msnums
    if msprimes[p]
      msps << p
      for q in msnums
        pq = p * q
        break if pq > max_p
        msprimes[pq] = false
      end
    end
  end

  msps
end

def sieve (n):

	ms_prime += [1 for i in range(n-5)]
	ub = math.sqrt(n) + 1
	d = 6
	while d <= ub:

			d += 1

			d += 1
			continue
		prod = 2
		while d * prod <= n:
			ms_prime[d*prod] = 0
			prod += 1
		d += 1
	return ms_prime

def isms(num):
    if num % 7 == 1 or num % 7 == 6: return True
    else: return False

def ismsp(num):
    i = 1
    while True:
        item = 7 * i - 1
        if item > int(num / 6) + 1: break

        if num % item == 0: return False

        item = 7 * i + 1
        if item > int(num / 6) + 1: break

        if num % item == 0: return False

        i += 1
    return True
